ChecklistBank Index Builder
---------------------------

This project provides the checklistbank solr index. It is configured to build a shaded, executable jar which will build a full new solr index
from the postgres database using a configurabale amount of threads.

mvn install package will produce a shaded jar in your target dir named checklistbank-solr.jar.
To build a new index run the jar with a checklistbank.properties file containing the setttings for the clb db and indexing configs like this:

    java -Xmx4g -jar checklistbank-solr.jar ./checklistbank.properties

For required and valid property file settings see [resources/checklistbank.properties](resources/checklistbank.properties)

java -jar ~/Downloads/avro-tools-1.7.7.jar compile -string schema src/main/resources/solr.avrsc src/main/java/
